fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.reader

Interface Reader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InputNotifier<Processor>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractReader, AbstractXmiReader, XmiStreamReader

    public interface Reader
extends InputNotifier<Processor>
    An InputNotifier that reads data from a file.

    It correspond to the head of the parsing process in case of an import.
